        {
            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I guess for cython the header files don't matter as long as they shouldn't trigger cython to re-compiler/transpile (at least from Meson's point of view) as the C/C++ compiler will generate its own depfile that would cover the inclusion of C language headers, so for Meson I guess that just means pxd files?",
